            <div class="col-md-4"><div class="card card-quiet p-3"><h5>Open access</h5><p class="small text-muted mb-0">Anyone can join. Many connect free.</p></div></div>
            <div class="col-md-4"><div class="card card-quiet p-3"><h5>Commons license</h5><p class="small text-muted mb-0">Shared rules keep it neutral.</p></div></div>
            <div class="col-md-4"><div class="card card-quiet p-3"><h5>Community‑led</h5><p class="small text-muted mb-0">Neighbors install and govern it.</p></div></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<section id="features" class="section bg-white border-top border-bottom">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center mb-4">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">Why it works</h2>
            <p class="text-muted">Simple gear. Short links. Clear rules.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row g-3">
            <div class="col-md-4"><div class="card card-quiet p-3 h-100"><h5>Mesh first</h5><p class="small text-muted mb-0">Every node helps others reach the net.</p></div></div>
            <div class="col-md-4"><div class="card card-quiet p-3 h-100"><h5>Resilient paths</h5><p class="small text-muted mb-0">Multiple routes keep traffic flowing.</p></div></div>
            <div class="col-md-4"><div class="card card-quiet p-3 h-100"><h5>Open hardware</h5><p class="small text-muted mb-0">Commodity gear. Easy to maintain.</p></div></div>
            <div class="col-md-4"><div class="card card-quiet p-3 h-100"><h5>Scales local</h5><p class="small text-muted mb-0">Hubs and relays serve whole blocks.</p></div></div>
